Who's News:
   Markel Corp. Gives
   Two Top Positions
   To Anthony Markel
Additionally, Joseph J. Prochaska Jr., 41, was named
executive vice president of operations in a newly created
position. Darrell D. Martin, 43, was named an executive vice
president. Mr. Martin will continue to serve as chief
financial officer.
   Milton and Stanley Markel, the respective fathers of
Anthony and Steven Markel, are currently consultants with the
firm. Their grandfather, Samuel Markel, founded the business
in 1930.